<p class="ql-align-justify">／法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/63134267edeb4c3897ac2e38bf6bf539.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 冠军战队联名的奶茶店 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201124/f19c363245e646b08a99b7de19f5cd14.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201124/511d1ab68f8847aead20fa8d308a105a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这间奶茶店什么来头？居然<strong>把刺激战场搬来了花城汇</strong>，请你吃鸡就算了，还要请你喝奶茶？...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201124/4ddc32e2b6074470aa15e003354a7746.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201124/7a379b47126f4af3a35768a00aa0176b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201124/8b109251e9d646acb322462aa960656d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内“吃鸡”的元素随处可见，还有一整面墙大的屏幕播放着游戏视频，<strong>爱玩吃鸡的人来到这一定超激动</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/af404db2c64d45e599e33ce3d0f85a4d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">惊喜还没完！它可不是随便蹭游戏热度的奶茶店，竟然是<strong>绝地求生冠军战队OMG联名的奶茶研饮室</strong>！粉丝们还在等什么，快点来GET大神同款呀~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 来这喝奶茶，撞星率超高 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201124/159643f8afbd4817829a40372c37eda3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201124/7f5daada3694444d88691e926b3ac039.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• OMG，『芒芒优格乳酸』登陆了！•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/5adf39c8f4144e4f819a2e96185e152f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">别小看这个可爱的小胖瓶！这款『OMG水果优格』用新鲜水果搭配酸奶，<strong>既有奶茶的口感，又比奶茶低糖健康</strong>，怪不得<strong>连明星都为它打call</strong>!</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• OMG，料也太多了吧！•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/ed98e0a8c0be47d59a6adaf0fd917b63.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>胖嘟嘟的一瓶有足足四层料</strong>，怪不得吸起来口感那么丰富，每一层都能给味蕾带来不同的美妙体验~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>第①层 | 优格 - 酸酸甜甜，软滑细腻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201124/3f621d03b47a42448af29fd8fdff74b1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>第②层 | 水果切片 - 清新果香</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201124/7d70ab8bf1b6419ead7ab4f1b25e486c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>第③层 | 芒果泥 - 绵密浓郁，口感满分</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201124/6039181d5ad143c4b49cf21d8ed07208.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201124/40831324f8634d678c4b9834efd7180f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>第④层 | 低卡寒天茶冻 - Q弹爽滑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201124/ca86fd910d8c4dadb4c07e9b698a1e1c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201124/e3efd152d40846c9846f05cf7830244d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>酸酸甜甜很好入口，满满的配料嗦着嗦着就停不下来了</strong>！吸到一杯见底，还要打包一杯带走才过瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/c3963b5401974222a392b16b1c8676c8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 维 C 满满波波茶 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201124/dbb2de91ecad4a208a55dbabae12cf5b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201124/b85e08988b4e4061bd26999061c34a67.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201124/9793919e0bb24f6790c34a6ad7bca2e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">别再说茶饮不健康啦！<strong>这一杯波波茶满满都是维C</strong>，火龙果、芒果、猕猴桃、橙子...光是水果都有好几种！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 莓莓荔枝气泡水 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201124/2159999eb9ca4fffa22b1be736998884.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201124/b76b03ae9d854ebcbade772e405a3a4d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201124/40f3785eb5c44a4c92028144558e3d6b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">想要抓住广州的夏天，一杯清爽的气泡水再适合不过。可尔必思乳酸菌冰沙带来酸甜滋味，混合草莓香气，<strong>满口的香甜清新</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 椰香桃桃茶 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201124/b340aeaf958b468896d89c17252258f1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201124/417501ddf52b42cc8241526f45c2cb43.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/75bd6ca15e0347e382f00ed6519ee38b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这一杯拿到手，它就用<strong>粉粉的颜值</strong>征服小编的少女心啦！椰冻一下子就滑入口腔，然后是绵软丰厚的桃肉冰沙，<strong>清爽不腻</strong>，再来两杯都不够！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 经典豆豆茶 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/7ad061b1eba640a79a58506082ff01fe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201124/db8f99e43e0f40deac2b88caa2c3abda.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201124/ae7b9b2924494d0c8dc3a6d260e1a15b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">豆奶爱好者千万不能错过这款！新鲜豆奶搭配奶油、奶冻</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 玫瑰普洱奶霜茶 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201124/4a2f740460164c94ad1dee2c5eca43e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201124/ce22eddf5e614f91a34cd9e0cf4ed7bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201124/be8ac935458c4e84826e28d2b588ff1c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">别看走眼啦，这可不是芝麻煳！是<strong>绝地吃鸡的特色奶霜</strong>，尝起来<strong>奶香味十足</strong>，咸甜的滋味和清香茶底超搭，吸起来还能嚼到Q弹的芋圆哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201124/24463714261d4fa7be4bc0562f167e0b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201124/6751a091326c43c5b10f9b98f1bd476d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">能够边喝奶茶边打“吃鸡”已经够爽的了！没想到来这<strong>还能吃到真的鸡，</strong>而且还是从韩国学来的<strong>正宗韩式炸鸡</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 新鲜现炸，酥香多汁 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201124/51c9fd949dae435db73cbfb87934b73d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">新鲜的无骨鸡块<strong>现点现炸</strong>，外皮香脆，内里还能保持肉嫩多汁！尝过之后，炸鸡在我心里的官配<strong>就从啤酒变成奶茶了...</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 一边吃炸鸡，一边“吃鸡” •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201124/22aa5d440e0c451291671fcad5e44fed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201124/a1ecacba44a349099b1873bd59589568.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">又能喝奶茶，又能吃炸鸡，就连来这打“吃鸡”都更有氛围了！还等什么，快叫上朋友<strong>一起登陆这个奶茶届的“刺激战场”</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201124/b1d4067a34454225ade181c2b7c27894.png" max-width="600" /></p>
